  nv:["Not every pigmented lesion is sinister. Recognising the hallmarks of a benign naevus is as important as identifying melanoma.","The regular reticular pattern with peripheral fading is dermoscopy's most satisfying benign signature.","Training your eye to recognise normal is the foundation upon which you identify the abnormal."],
